SUMMARY:IMPROMPTU CoffeeTue- LI Scratch Bakes (28R) -- RSVP required
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nRide Leader: Bruce Black\
 n\nCoffeeTue rides:\n• A rotating start location\, not a school\n• A p
 redetermined route\n• 25+/- mile routes\n• 13 to 15 mph average pace\n
 • Usually no sweep\n• “short” stop for refreshment/coffee mid-rout
 e at [Scratch Bakes Cafe](https://www.scratchbakes.com/)\n\nClick for [Rid
 e with GPS](https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/li-scratch-bakes-28r/
 )\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No ear buds. Please bring water and a basic re
 pair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nTo eliminate p
 assing around a pen and paper waiver\, we require LBC Club membership and 
 Meetup RSVP below to join this ride.\n\nBeing on Meetup does not mean you 
 are a club member. [Join here](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.a
 spx?page_id=60&club_id=257148).\n\nYour RSVP is your agreement to abide by
  the club's [Code of Conduct](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content
 .aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984) \,\n[Rules of the Road](
 https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=25714
 8&module_id=325159) \, and [Ride Waiver](https://lancasterbikeclub.net/doc
 s.ashx?id=454318)
